Intakes by Race Neighborhood-Level Report

February 26, 2021

Overall Summary

  • This report summarizes 5000 intakes with descision dates between 2020-01-01 and 2020-12-31.

  • 1000 intakes are missing allegation address. The most recently entered child address will be used.

  • 43 (0.9%) intakes had an address that was not able to be geocoded.

  • 1357 (58.6%) intakes of a White ACV were screened in. 957 (41.4%) intakes of a White ACV were screened out.

  • 1250 (59.8%) intakes of a Black/African American ACV were screened in. 841 (40.2%) intakes of a Black/African American ACV were screened out.

  • There were 556 intakes of neither a White nor Black/African American ACV.

  • 342 (62%) intakes of a Non-White nor Black/African American ACV were screened in. 210 (38%) intakes of a Non-White nor Black/African American ACV were screened out.
